sql:
SELECT
    dim_date_calendar_date,
    dim_date_calendar_month,
    fct_ga_channel_groupings_total_bounces
FROM
    (SELECT
            (dim_date.calendar_date ) AS dim_date_calendar_date,
            dim_date.calendar_month  AS dim_date_calendar_month,
            COALESCE(SUM(fct_ga_channel_groupings.total_bounces ), 0) AS fct_ga_channel_groupings_total_bounces,
            COALESCE(SUM(fct_ga_channel_groupings.total_bounces ), 0) AS fct_ga_channel_groupings_total_bounces_0
        FROM `dbt_jbrooks.fct_ga_channel_groupings`
     AS fct_ga_channel_groupings
INNER JOIN `dbt_jbrooks.dim_date`
     AS dim_date ON fct_ga_channel_groupings.visit_date = dim_date.calendar_date
        GROUP BY
            1,
            2
        HAVING fct_ga_channel_groupings_total_bounces_0 > 1500) AS t2
ORDER BY
    1 DESC
LIMIT 25
